					</div>
                    <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                        <h4>Workforce Optimization is simply put to be the art of holistically applying the science of individual human resources management techniques</h4>
                        <h4>This approach has a few driving factors which make the WO mindset such an important evolutionary step.</h4>
                    </div>
